00:41:20,880 --> 00:41:23,000
People are all self-centered.

537
00:41:23,000 --> 00:41:25,470
Are you any different?

538
00:41:25,470 --> 00:41:27,500
Gosh...

539
00:41:27,500 --> 00:41:31,340
I'm the idiot for coming here, thinking we'd be able to communicate.

540
00:41:31,340 --> 00:41:33,110
Crap.

541
00:41:42,510 --> 00:41:45,660
You came to meet that Ahjusshi? Who is he?

542
00:41:46,560 --> 00:41:49,410
So Hui, should we see Oppa before we go?

543
00:41:49,410 --> 00:41:50,700
Mom!

544
00:41:50,700 --> 00:41:54,950
We came all the way here. Wouldn't Oppa be sad if we left without seeing him?

545
00:41:54,950 --> 00:41:58,590
We came because you said you'll feel better if you see the ocean.

546
00:41:58,590 --> 00:42:02,070
Is this the true reason why you wanted to come to Busan?

547
00:42:02,070 --> 00:42:04,180
No, that's not it.

548
00:42:04,180 --> 00:42:06,980
I always liked the ocean.

549
00:42:07,820 --> 00:42:10,880
I'd like to live by the ocean if I can.

550
00:42:12,890 --> 00:42:14,950
Don't you?

551
00:42:19,820 --> 00:42:22,780
Dad, Dad!

552
00:42:22,780 --> 00:42:24,910
Dad, give me a marker!

553
00:42:34,400 --> 00:42:35,400
What are you doing?

554
00:42:35,400 --> 00:42:39,870
Even if it was for commercial use, this is way too flashy.

555
00:42:39,870 --> 00:42:41,900
Hey, this much is fine.

556
00:42:41,900 --> 00:42:44,700
- Dal, eat some scallion pancake inside. 
 - Pardon?

557
00:42:48,550 --> 00:42:50,380
   

558
00:42:53,100 --> 00:42:54,820
I need to take this call.

559
00:42:54,820 --> 00:42:57,870
How is his pose so cool?

560
00:42:57,870 --> 00:43:00,410
He exudes a bright light.

561
00:43:01,500 --> 00:43:02,840
Did San Ha go to work?

562
00:43:02,840 --> 00:43:04,620
Yes, he wants some scallion pancakes, too.

563
00:43:04,620 --> 00:43:06,520
All right. I got it.

564
00:43:07,710 --> 00:43:09,980
Why isn't Dal coming? Let me go get her.

565
00:43:09,980 --> 00:43:13,160
No, you eat. I'll go get her.

566
00:43:18,380 --> 00:43:19,520
That's not it.

567
00:43:19,520 --> 00:43:21,630
 What can you do on your own? 

568
00:43:21,630 --> 00:43:24,330
 Even if you have a man, you should pretend not to have one on those blind dates. 

569
00:43:24,330 --> 00:43:25,970
 Do I have to teach you that, too? 

570
00:43:25,970 --> 00:43:28,400
I said I'm sorry about that.

571
00:43:28,400 --> 00:43:30,040
He behaved badly, too!

572
00:43:30,040 --> 00:43:31,710
 Stop blaming others. 

573
00:43:31,710 --> 00:43:35,720
 If you won't work in a law firm in Seoul, you should marry well for me to feel relieved. 

574
00:43:35,720 --> 00:43:37,940
I'm doing just fine here.

575
00:43:37,940 --> 00:43:39,320
You can be relieved.

576
00:43:39,320 --> 00:43:42,880
 I need to see you live a good life like others to feel relieved! 

577
00:43:45,380 --> 00:43:47,360
I'm sorry.

578
00:43:50,400 --> 00:43:54,030
Mom, I sent you some money to buy spring clothes.

579
00:43:54,030 --> 00:43:56,100
Did you get it?

580
00:43:58,090 --> 00:43:59,590
Yes.

581
00:44:02,050 --> 00:44:03,490
   

582
00:44:31,310 --> 00:44:33,940
I didn't mean to eavesdrop.

583
00:44:36,330 --> 00:44:38,170
It's because of me, right?

584
00:44:39,310 --> 00:44:41,740
Should I have said something else?

585
00:44:42,850 --> 00:44:45,640
The call dragged on.

586
00:44:46,860 --> 00:44:48,730
I'm hungry.

587
00:44:48,730 --> 00:44:50,860
Let's go inside.

588
00:44:57,240 --> 00:44:59,530
- Joo Won. 
 - Yes?

589
00:45:02,730 --> 00:45:04,500
Take a bite.

590
00:45:07,690 --> 00:45:09,240
Is it okay?

591
00:45:09,950 --> 00:45:12,630
It's the best. It's awesome.

592
00:45:12,630 --> 00:45:15,340
- Joo Won. 
 - Yes.

593
00:45:16,110 --> 00:45:17,730
Hurry up and come eat.

594
00:45:17,730 --> 00:45:19,600
- Scallion pancake. 
 - Is it good?

595
00:45:19,600 --> 00:45:21,750
The fresh kimchi is great.

596
00:45:21,750 --> 00:45:23,910
Let's take a ton home.

597
00:45:23,910 --> 00:45:28,150
I'll pack you scallion pancakes and fresh kimchi later. Take them.

598
00:45:28,150 --> 00:45:30,020
Oh, yes!

599
00:45:33,530 --> 00:45:36,640
Everyone, the model is here!

600
00:45:37,830 --> 00:45:39,730
Line up here if you want an autograph.

601
00:45:39,730 --> 00:45:42,850
- I want one! 
 - Me, too!

602
00:45:42,850 --> 00:45:44,920
- One for me, too! 
 - Make a line.

603
00:45:44,920 --> 00:45:46,450
How nice!

604
00:45:46,450 --> 00:45:49,290
Let me take a look.

605
00:45:49,290 --> 00:45:52,070
My goodness. Even your autograph is amazing.

606
00:45:52,070 --> 00:45:54,910
Sign my handkerchief here.

607
00:45:55,540 --> 00:45:57,830
Was it Ahjumma?

608
00:45:58,500 --> 00:46:00,380
Yes.

609
00:46:00,380 --> 00:46:03,930
Don't force yourself if you don't have an appetite and give it to me.

610
00:46:06,310 --> 00:46:08,750
- Thanks. 
 - Thank you.

611
00:46:11,010 --> 00:46:12,730
What should we have with fresh kimchi for dinner?

612
00:46:12,730 --> 00:46:14,390
Parboiled octopus? Half-dried mackerel?

613
00:46:14,390 --> 00:46:17,520
Or should I boil some pork belly? A drink?

614
00:46:18,170 --> 00:46:20,340
It's not like this is the first time.

615
00:46:20,340 --> 00:46:24,470
I think I'll be late because I was away from the office this morning.

616
00:46:24,470 --> 00:46:28,980
All right. Let's eat something delicious tomorrow, then.

617
00:46:29,890 --> 00:46:31,580
Take care.

618
00:46:37,880 --> 00:46:41,440
   

619
00:46:43,830 --> 00:46:45,250
   

620
00:46:47,000 --> 00:46:48,360
Yes. Hello?

621
00:46:48,360 --> 00:46:50,590
 Hae Joon's excited, right? 

622
00:46:50,590 --> 00:46:54,440
You know Kang Hae Joon's fine as long as Dad is happy.

623
00:46:55,450 --> 00:47:00,370
I think I'll get off early today. At about seven o'clock.

624
00:47:00,370 --> 00:47:02,540
Do you want to have dinner with me?

625
00:47:02,540 --> 00:47:04,180
"Dinner"?

626
00:47:04,980 --> 00:47:06,390
What are we going to have?

627
00:47:06,390 --> 00:47:08,370
I'll look into it.

628
00:47:08,370 --> 00:47:11,560
Well, shall we, then?

629
00:47:11,560 --> 00:47:13,230
Yes.

630
00:47:17,200 --> 00:47:18,810
What's this?

631
00:47:18,810 --> 00:47:21,300
Why are you suddenly smiling? Is something good going on?

632
00:47:21,300 --> 00:47:23,960
Do you know any place for dinner nearby?

633
00:47:23,960 --> 00:47:27,160
"Dinner"? What's the occasion?

634
00:47:27,880 --> 00:47:29,550
A date.

635
00:47:30,490 --> 00:47:33,600
Do you have a girlfriend? Daebak.

636
00:47:33,600 --> 00:47:35,250
Hey, who is it?

637
00:47:35,250 --> 00:47:38,020
- Gosh, stop it. 
 - Hey, who is it? Tell me.

638
00:47:38,020 --> 00:47:40,850
There are tons of models in the U.S.

639
00:47:40,850 --> 00:47:44,480
It's not like I was that famous. I only took a few pictures and stopped.

640
00:47:44,480 --> 00:47:47,600
You should've done some more if you had fun.

641
00:47:47,600 --> 00:47:50,600
I would've if I knew you'd be this happy.

642
00:47:52,470 --> 00:47:56,940
I'm happy you're healthy.

643
00:47:56,940 --> 00:48:00,070
You must be hungry. Eat at home before you go, if you have time.

644
00:48:00,070 --> 00:48:01,480
Okay.

645
00:48:17,300 --> 00:48:20,240
Seok Hoon wants to see me.

646
00:48:20,240 --> 00:48:22,910
I'll come to eat next time.

647
00:48:22,910 --> 00:48:25,820
Why? Eat if it's not urgent.

648
00:48:25,820 --> 00:48:29,090
He said the entire basketball team was there to eat together.

649
00:48:29,090 --> 00:48:31,510
All right. Come tomorrow, then.

650
00:48:31,510 --> 00:48:34,560
Yes. I'll get going.

651
00:48:39,460 --> 00:48:42,440
 I gave this a lot of thought. 

652
00:48:42,440 --> 00:48:46,900
 But I just can't forget your face that day. 

653
00:48:46,900 --> 00:48:49,260
 So I told her you're back here. 

654
00:48:49,260 --> 00:48:52,600
 It's up to you if you want to go see her or not. 

655
00:48:52,600 --> 00:48:54,380
Taxi!

656
00:49:16,980 --> 00:49:18,660
Take care.

657
00:49:25,790 --> 00:49:27,540
- Boss. 
 - Yes?

658
00:49:27,540 --> 00:49:30,200
Why are you in such a good mood these days?

659
00:49:30,200 --> 00:49:33,070
Really? Do I look happy?

660
00:49:33,070 --> 00:49:34,630
Yes.

661
00:50:15,040 --> 00:50:19,880
 I'll bring your favorite hamburgers when I come back, Hae Joon. 

662
00:50:38,640 --> 00:50:41,450
So frustrating. Aigoo.

663
00:50:42,890 --> 00:50:46,760
You should've at least said something for your child's sake.

664
00:50:46,760 --> 00:50:49,130
I'll take care of it. Mind your own business.

665
00:50:49,130 --> 00:50:51,430
And if I do?

666
00:50:53,240 --> 00:50:59,410
I mean, I'll make sure to try talking to her again.

667
00:51:01,220 --> 00:51:04,920
What about you? What will you tell Hae Joo's mom?

668
00:51:04,920 --> 00:51:06,080
What do you think?

669
00:51:06,080 --> 00:51:09,910
I'll tell her to come see Hae Joon, who has grown up nicely.

670
00:51:10,800 --> 00:51:14,790
I'm different from you-know-who. I keep my word.

671
00:51:16,600 --> 00:51:18,900
We will see about that!

672
00:51:55,350 --> 00:51:56,900
Did you wait?

673
00:51:56,900 --> 00:51:58,450
No.

674
00:52:07,830 --> 00:52:09,290
What?

675
00:52:09,290 --> 00:52:11,670
Someone might see.

676
00:52:12,740 --> 00:52:15,590
I'll see Dad this weekend and tell him everything.

677
00:52:19,180 --> 00:52:22,760
About that... Should we tell Kang Hae Joon first?

678
00:52:22,760 --> 00:52:24,560
What does he know?

679
00:52:24,560 --> 00:52:28,560
Not that he'd know anything. I just don't want him to be upset later.

680
00:52:34,830 --> 00:52:36,690
Isn't that Kang Hae Joon?

681
00:52:43,160 --> 00:52:44,810
As expected of model Kang.

682
00:52:44,810 --> 00:52:46,630
You're just sitting, and it's still a photoshoot.

683
00:52:46,630 --> 00:52:48,770
Hey, extend your leg–

684
00:52:58,620 --> 00:53:00,240
What is it?

685
00:53:03,270 --> 00:53:05,150
Is something wrong?

686
00:53:07,490 --> 00:53:09,420
I saw Mom.

687
00:53:14,370 --> 00:53:16,030
Where?

688
00:53:17,820 --> 00:53:20,530
Auntie told me she opened...

689
00:53:21,580 --> 00:53:23,770
a hair salon in Busan.

690
00:53:26,830 --> 00:53:28,410
And?

691
00:53:28,970 --> 00:53:31,460
What did she say when she met you?

692
00:53:35,270 --> 00:53:37,190
I didn't meet her.

693
00:53:37,190 --> 00:53:39,740
I only saw her from afar.

694
00:53:47,630 --> 00:53:49,900
She smiled brightly...

695
00:53:52,020 --> 00:53:54,250
and seemed to be doing well.

696
00:54:00,580 --> 00:54:02,220
Get up.

697
00:54:03,930 --> 00:54:05,330
What?

698
00:54:06,130 --> 00:54:09,580
Go ask her why she never contacted you.

699
00:54:09,580 --> 00:54:11,770
If you can't do it alone, I'll come with you.

700
00:54:11,770 --> 00:54:13,570
No, I'll do it for you. Get up!

701
00:54:13,570 --> 00:54:16,470
Stop acting so pitiful and get up!

702
00:54:17,300 --> 00:54:19,840
Hey, I can't ask her that.

703
00:54:19,840 --> 00:54:22,020
Why can't you?

704
00:54:23,720 --> 00:54:26,040
I'm not prepared to hear her answer.

705
00:54:28,300 --> 00:54:30,780
I'm too scared to ask her.

706
00:54:31,420 --> 00:54:33,150
Let's head inside.

707
00:54:43,260 --> 00:54:46,350
Are you hungry? Should we order delivery?

708
00:54:47,520 --> 00:54:48,950
You two can eat.

709
00:54:48,950 --> 00:54:51,250
I'm a bit tired today.

710
00:54:57,080 --> 00:54:59,570
I feel better with both of you, though.

711
00:55:13,810 --> 00:55:15,350
What?

712
00:55:27,920 --> 00:55:29,420
Did you find it?

713
00:55:29,420 --> 00:55:33,430
Yeah, the address was in a text from Auntie.

714
00:55:48,320 --> 00:55:50,250
Hae Joon has been–

715
00:55:54,450 --> 00:55:56,100
Dad!

716
00:55:58,460 --> 00:56:00,690
How did you know about this place?

717
00:56:00,690 --> 00:56:03,480
How did you two...

718
00:56:34,970 --> 00:56:36,770
Where did they go?

719
00:56:44,350 --> 00:56:46,440
Did I leave this here?

720
00:56:48,620 --> 00:56:50,670
Who is it?

721
00:56:56,290 --> 00:56:59,780
So that's why you never contacted Hae Joon?

722
00:56:59,780 --> 00:57:02,550
And why you don't plan to in the future?

723
00:57:03,560 --> 00:57:05,140
Yes.

724
00:57:05,140 --> 00:57:08,020
If Hae Joon finds out,

725
00:57:08,020 --> 00:57:10,820
you're willing to go wherever?

726
00:57:14,290 --> 00:57:17,560
Then why did you have to open this store in Busan?

727
00:57:19,760 --> 00:57:23,270
It just turned out like this.

728
00:57:23,270 --> 00:57:25,240
That's not it.

729
00:57:25,240 --> 00:57:27,850
It's because it's close to Hae Joon.

730
00:57:30,000 --> 00:57:33,660
So, does Hae Joon...

731
00:57:34,620 --> 00:57:37,330
Does Hae Joon also know that I'm here?

732
00:57:40,150 --> 00:57:41,820
He doesn't.

733
00:57:46,390 --> 00:57:48,530
Kang Hae Joon doesn't know.

734
00:57:49,490 --> 00:57:52,220
We came after hearing about it by coincidence.

735
00:57:53,550 --> 00:57:56,380
We didn't tell him about coming here...

736
00:57:57,350 --> 00:58:01,130
in case he'd be disappointed.

737
00:58:10,960 --> 00:58:14,760
Is it okay as long as you feel at ease?

738
00:58:14,760 --> 00:58:16,890
What about Kang Hae Joon?

739
00:58:16,890 --> 00:58:22,080
Kang Hae Joon lived his entire life in the dark, believing he was just baggage.

740
00:58:24,110 --> 00:58:27,080
Ever since you cut him off,

741
00:58:27,080 --> 00:58:30,000
he thought he was dead weight to you.

742
00:58:31,100 --> 00:58:34,800
People kept saying my dad took in a charity case!

743
00:58:34,800 --> 00:58:38,950
So he has thought of himself as an outsider for his entire life!

744
00:58:38,950 --> 00:58:41,030
Do you even know?

745
00:58:58,930 --> 00:59:00,870
Thank you.

746
00:59:15,050 --> 00:59:17,690
 Where are you? Are you at the hospital? 

747
00:59:17,690 --> 00:59:21,380
 Hurry home. Or call me when you see this. 

748
00:59:44,800 --> 00:59:47,280
Gosh, what are you doing, Seo Hyeon?

749
00:59:47,280 --> 00:59:50,770
I just want him to...

750
00:59:54,700 --> 00:59:58,220
live an ordinary life.

751
01:00:11,110 --> 01:00:21,050


752
01:00:26,180 --> 01:00:30,200
♫  One day  ♫

753
01:00:30,200 --> 01:00:34,200
♫  A precious memory  ♫

754
01:00:34,200 --> 01:00:40,920
♫  Entered my small heart the day you smiled brightly  ♫

755
01:00:41,870 --> 01:00:43,660
   

756
01:00:43,660 --> 01:00:46,480
 You abandoned me, lived happily, and even met a man. 

757
01:00:46,480 --> 01:00:48,190
 Should I not have shown up in your great life? 

758
01:00:48,190 --> 01:00:50,100
 How did you find this place? 

759
01:00:50,100 --> 01:00:52,480
 - Pretend you never saw me today. 
 - I'm sorry. 

760
01:00:52,480 --> 01:00:55,920
 I've made up my mind, and I'm never coming back. 

761
01:00:57,280 --> 01:00:58,920
 You even changed the hospital? 

762
01:00:58,920 --> 01:01:03,150
 So you'll be selfish until the end and do what you want? 

763
01:01:03,150 --> 01:01:05,990
 Must you see me die? 

764
01:01:05,990 --> 01:01:09,200
 Take So Hui and go back to Seoul. 

765
01:01:09,200 --> 01:01:10,360
 I'm not going. 

766
01:01:10,360 --> 01:01:13,900
 San Ha's mom seemed determined to take San Ha with her. 

767
01:01:13,900 --> 01:01:16,780
 If you're staying here because of me, it's okay. 

768
01:01:16,780 --> 01:01:20,460
 I won't say stay by my side or stay here. 

769
01:01:26,720 --> 01:01:29,230
♫  Maybe...   ♫

